---
  <section id="about" class="py-24 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-white/5">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-16">关于我</h2>
      
      <div class="space-y-20">
        <!-- 01. Experience -->
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
          <div class="text-accent font-mono text-sm tracking-widest uppercase pt-1">01. 经历</div>
          <div class="md:col-span-3 space-y-12">
            <div class="relative pl-6 border-l border-gray-200 dark:border-white/10">
              <div class="mb-10 relative">
                 <span class="absolute -left-[29px] top-1.5 w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-blue-500 ring-4 ring-white dark:ring-primary"></span>
                 <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">AI架构师</h3>
                 <div class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-2">Lenovo · 联想XXX院</div>

              </div>
              <div class="mb-10 relative">
                 <span class="absolute -left-[29px] top-1.5 w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-gray-700 ring-4 ring-white dark:ring-primary"></span>
                 <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">AI高级开发工程师</h3>
                 <div class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-2">Baidu · 百度</div>
              </div>
              <div class="relative">
                 <span class="absolute -left-[29px] top-1.5 w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-gray-700 ring-4 ring-white dark:ring-primary"></span>
                 <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">硕士学位</h3>
                 <div class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-2">CASIA · 中科院自动化所</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 02. Philosophy -->
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
           <div class="text-accent font-mono text-sm tracking-widest uppercase pt-1">02. 理念</div>
           <div class="md:col-span-3">
             <p class="text-xl text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 leading-relaxed mb-6 font-light">
               "AI handles the syntax. I focus on the product."
             </p>
             <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed text-base">
               我相信 <strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Vibe Coding</strong> 是一种新的心流状态。
               不需要记住所有 API，不需要去 Stack Overflow 复制粘贴。
               我们用自然语言编排逻辑，用 Cursor 生成骨架，用 Claude 注入灵魂。
               这不仅仅是效率的提升，更是创造力的解放。
             </p>
           </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 03. Tech Stack -->
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
           <div class="text-accent font-mono text-sm tracking-widest uppercase pt-1">03. 技术栈</div>
           <div class="md:col-span-3">
             <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-8 gap-y-4 font-mono text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
               <div class="space-y-2">
                 <div class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white text-xs opacity-50 mb-1">CORE</div>
                 <div>Python / TypeScript</div>
               </div>
               <div class="space-y-2">
                 <div class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white text-xs opacity-50 mb-1">AI ENGINEERING</div>
                 <div>LangChain / LangGraph / RAG</div>
               </div>
               <div class="space-y-2">
                 <div class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white text-xs opacity-50 mb-1">FRAMEWORKS</div>
                 <div>React / Next.js / Astro</div>
               </div>
               <div class="space-y-2">
                 <div class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white text-xs opacity-50 mb-1">TOOLS</div>
                 <div>Cursor / Claude / Docker</div>
               </div>
             </div>
           </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
